data.description: Welcome home to this lovely, freshly-painted 3-bedroom, 2.5-bath home in Southwest Licking school district.  This home is in the USDA eligible area and can be bought with no money down! It has 2 living areas and a large eat-in kitchen with updated backsplash.  All bedrooms are upstairs, including the owner's bedroom and ensuite. Full unfinished basement with endless possibilities!  Nice-sized, private fenced in backyard for all kinds of fun! All with walking distance to the park.
